<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Brandify Business Solutions — We Brand. We Grow. We Deliver Results.</title>
<meta name="description" content="Brandify Business Solutions builds brand identity, digital marketing, and lead generation systems for businesses ready to grow.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0A0D14;
    --bg-alt:#12151F;
    --bg-alt-2:#181C29;
    --ink:#F3F1EA;
    --ink-soft:#9CA3B5;
    --gold:#D9A94E;
    --gold-soft:#F0CD82;
    --cobalt:#3D5CFF;
    --green:#33B47A;
    --coral:#FF6B4A;
    --line: rgba(243,241,234,0.12);
    --font-display:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    --font-body:'Inter', sans-serif;
    --font-mono:'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    --max: 1160px;
  }

  *{ box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }
  body{
    background:var(--bg);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:var(--font-body);
    line-height:1.5;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  img{ max-width:100%; display:block; }
  a{ color:inherit; }
  ul{ list-style:none; }
  section{ scroll-margin-top:84px; }

  ::selection{ background:var(--gold); color:var(--bg); }

  a:focus-visible, button:focus-visible, input:focus-visible, textarea:focus-visible{
    outline:2px solid var(--gold);
    outline-offset:3px;
  }

  .wrap{ max-width:var(--max); margin:0 auto; padding:0 32px; }

  .eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:0.72rem;
    letter-spacing:0.14em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--gold);
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:8px;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{
    content:"";
    width:6px; height:6px;
    background:var(--gold);
    display:inline-block;
  }

  h1,h2,h3{ font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  .nav{
    position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100;
    background:rgba(10,13,20,0.86);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav__inner{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    height:76px;
  }
  .nav__mark{
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:700; font-size:1.15rem;
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    text-decoration:none;
  }
  .nav__logo-icon{
    height:38px; width:auto; border-radius:6px; display:block; object-fit:cover;
  }
  .nav__links{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:32px;
  }
  .nav__links a{
    font-size:0.9rem; text-decoration:none; color:var(--ink-soft);
    transition:color .15s ease;
  }
  .nav__links a:hover{ color:var(--ink); }
  .nav__cta{
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.78rem;
    background:var(--gold); color:var(--bg);
    padding:10px 18px;
    text-decoration:none;
    white-space:nowrap;
    font-weight:500;
    transition:background .15s ease;
  }
  .nav__cta:hover{ background:var(--gold-soft); }
  .nav__toggle{
    display:none;
    background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer;
    width:32px; height:24px; position:relative;
  }
  .nav__toggle span{
    position:absolute; left:0; right:0; height:2px; background:var(--ink);
    transition:transform .2s ease, opacity .2s ease;
  }
  .nav__toggle span:nth-child(1){ top:0; }
  .nav__toggle span:nth-child(2){ top:11px; }
  .nav__toggle span:nth-child(3){ top:22px; }
  .nav--open .nav__toggle span:nth-child(1){ transform:translateY(11px) rotate(45deg); }
  .nav--open .nav__toggle span:nth-child(2){ opacity:0; }
  .nav--open .nav__toggle span:nth-child(3){ transform:translateY(-11px) rotate(-45deg); }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero{ padding:160px 0 100px; }
  .hero__inner{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.05fr 0.85fr;
    gap:64px;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 4.2vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height:1.1;
    margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .hero h1 .line-gold{ color:var(--gold); }
  .hero p.lead{
    font-size:1.06rem;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
    max-width:46ch;
    margin-bottom:34px;
  }
  .hero__ctas{ display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .btn{
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
    font-size:0.85rem;
    padding:14px 24px;
    text-decoration:none;
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:8px;
    border:1px solid var(--gold);
    transition:background .15s ease, color .15s ease, border-color .15s ease;
  }
  .btn--primary{ background:var(--gold); color:var(--bg); font-weight:500; }
  .btn--primary:hover{ background:var(--gold-soft); border-color:var(--gold-soft); }
  .btn--ghost{ background:transparent; color:var(--ink); border-color:var(--line); }
  .btn--ghost:hover{ border-color:var(--gold); color:var(--gold); }

  .hero__logo{
    width:170px; max-width:55%; height:auto; border-radius:10px;
    margin-bottom:26px; box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
  }

  /* ---------- DASHBOARD CARD (signature element) ---------- */
  .dash-card{
    background:var(--bg-alt);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:28px;
    border-radius:4px;
  }
  .dash-card__head{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.06em;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom:14px; margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .dash-card__live{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; color:var(--green); }
  .dot-pulse{
    width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--green);
    animation:pulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse{
    0%,100%{ opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
    50%{ opacity:0.45; transform:scale(0.75); }
  }
  .dash-card__stats{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:14px;
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .stat{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:4px; }
  .stat__label{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.62rem; color:var(--ink-soft); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em; }
  .stat__value{ font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:600; }
  .stat__delta{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.68rem; color:var(--green); }
  .dash-card__chart{ margin-bottom:18px; }
  .dash-card__chart svg{ width:100%; height:70px; display:block; }
  .dash-card__foot{
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--ink-soft);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:16px;
  }
  .dash-card__foot strong{ color:var(--gold); font-weight:500; }

  /* ---------- PROBLEM ---------- */
  .problem{ padding:100px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg-alt); }
  .problem__inner{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr; gap:64px; }
  .problem h2{ font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem); line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .problem p.lead{ color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:1.02rem; max-width:52ch; margin-bottom:32px; }
  .reasons{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:18px; margin-bottom:32px; }
  .reason{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
  .reason__icon{
    width:38px; height:38px; flex:none; border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    border:1px solid rgba(217,169,78,0.35); color:var(--gold);
    background:rgba(217,169,78,0.08);
  }
  .reason__icon svg{ width:18px; height:18px; }
  .reason__text{ font-size:0.98rem; }
  .callout{
    border:1px solid rgba(217,169,78,0.4);
    padding:26px;
    display:flex; gap:18px; align-items:flex-start;
    background:rgba(217,169,78,0.06);
  }
  .callout__icon{
    width:46px; height:46px; flex:none; border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    background:var(--gold); color:var(--bg);
  }
  .callout__icon svg{ width:22px; height:22px; }
  .callout h3{ font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .callout h3 span{ color:var(--gold); }
  .callout p{ color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:0.94rem; }
  .zigzag{ margin-top:8px; }

  /* ---------- ABOUT ---------- */
  .about{ padding:100px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .about__inner{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:0.6fr 0.4fr; gap:64px; }
  .about h2{ font-size:clamp(1.7rem,2.6vw,2.3rem); line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .about p{ color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:1.02rem; max-width:56ch; }
  .about p + p{ margin-top:16px; }
  .about__tags{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; justify-content:center; }
  .about__tag{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.82rem; border-left:2px solid var(--gold); padding-left:14px; }

  /* ---------- SERVICES ---------- */
  .services{ padding:100px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg-alt); }
  .section-head{ margin-bottom:56px; max-width:60ch; }
  .section-head h2{ font-size:clamp(1.7rem,2.6vw,2.3rem); }
  .services__grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap:1px;
    background:var(--line);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .service-card{
    background:var(--bg-alt);
    padding:30px;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px;
    opacity:0; transform:translateY(16px);
    transition:opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease;
  }
  .service-card.is-visible{ opacity:1; transform:none; }
  .service-card__icon{
    width:44px; height:44px; border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    flex:none;
  }
  .service-card__icon svg{ width:20px; height:20px; }
  .service-card h3{ font-size:1.08rem; }
  .service-card p{ color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:0.9rem; }

  /* ---------- WHY US ---------- */
  .why{ padding:90px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .why__grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:20px;
  }
  .why-item{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;
    border:1px solid var(--line); padding:18px 20px;
  }
  .why-item svg{ width:18px; height:18px; color:var(--gold); flex:none; }
  .why-item span{ font-size:0.94rem; }

  /* ---------- PROCESS ---------- */
  .process{ padding:100px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg-alt); }
  .process__grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:40px; }
  .step{ position:relative; padding-top:20px; }
  .step__num{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--gold); display:block; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .step h3{ font-size:1.12rem; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .step p{ color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:0.94rem; }
  .step::before{ content:""; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:32px; height:1px; background:var(--gold); }

  /* ---------- PRICING ---------- */
  .pricing{ padding:100px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .pricing__grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:28px; }
  .price-card{
    border:1px solid var(--line); padding:34px; background:var(--bg-alt);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:18px;
  }
  .price-card--pro{ border-color:rgba(217,169,78,0.5); background:linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(217,169,78,0.08), var(--bg-alt) 60%); position:relative; }
  .price-card__badge{
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.68rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--gold); border:1px solid rgba(217,169,78,0.4); padding:5px 12px; align-self:flex-start;
  }
  .price-card h3{ font-size:1.3rem; }
  .price-card__amount{ font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:2.2rem; font-weight:700; }
  .price-card__amount span{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--ink-soft); font-weight:400; }
  .price-card__features{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; flex:1; }
  .price-card__features li{ display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start; font-size:0.92rem; color:var(--ink-soft); }
  .price-card__features li svg{ width:16px; height:16px; color:var(--gold); flex:none; margin-top:3px; }
  .pricing__note{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.78rem; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:20px; }

  /* ---------- DM BAND ---------- */
  .dmband{
    padding:56px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    background:var(--gold); color:var(--bg);
  }
  .dmband__inner{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:24px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .dmband h2{ font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.4vw,1.9rem); }
  .dmband p{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.85rem; }
  .dmband .btn{ border-color:var(--bg); }
  .dmband .btn--primary{ background:var(--bg); color:var(--gold-soft); border-color:var(--bg); }
  .dmband .btn--primary:hover{ background:#000; }

  /* ---------- CONTACT ---------- */
  .contact{ padding:100px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--bg-alt); }
  .contact__inner{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr; gap:64px; }
  .contact h2{ font-size:clamp(1.7rem,2.6vw,2.3rem); margin-bottom:18px; }
  .contact p.lead{ color:var(--ink-soft); max-width:44ch; margin-bottom:26px; }
  .contact__detail{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.88rem; margin-bottom:12px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
  .contact__detail svg{ width:16px; height:16px; color:var(--gold); flex:none; }
  .contact__detail a{ text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .contact__detail a:hover{ border-color:var(--gold); color:var(--gold); }

  form{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:18px; }
  .form-row{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:18px; }
  label{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.72rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--ink-soft); display:block; margin-bottom:8px; }
  input, textarea{
    width:100%; background:transparent; border:none; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:10px 2px; font-family:var(--font-body); font-size:0.98rem; color:var(--ink);
    transition:border-color .15s ease;
  }
  input:focus, textarea:focus{ border-color:var(--gold); outline:none; }
  textarea{ resize:vertical; min-height:90px; }
  .form-submit{
    margin-top:8px; align-self:flex-start; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.85rem;
    background:var(--gold); color:var(--bg); border:1px solid var(--gold); padding:14px 26px; cursor:pointer;
    transition:background .15s ease;
  }
  .form-submit:hover{ background:var(--gold-soft); border-color:var(--gold-soft); }
  .form-note{ font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:4px; }

  /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
  footer{ border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding:40px 0; }
  .footer__inner{ display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:16px; }
  .footer__mark{ font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:700; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
  .footer__logo-icon{ height:30px; width:auto; border-radius:5px; }
  .footer__meta{ font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:0.75rem; color:var(--ink-soft); display:flex; align-items:center; gap:18px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .footer__meta a{ text-decoration:none; }
  .footer__meta a:hover{ color:var(--gold); }

  .reveal{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease; }
  .reveal.is-visible{ opacity:1; transform:none; }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    html{ scroll-behavior:auto; }
    *{ transition:none !important; animation:none !important; }
    .reveal, .service-card{ opacity:1 !important; transform:none !important; }
  }

  @media (max-width:880px){
    .hero__inner{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .problem__inner{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .about__inner{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .contact__inner{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .services__grid{ grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
    .why__grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .process__grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:36px; }
    .pricing__grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width:720px){
    .nav__links{
      position:fixed; top:76px; left:0; right:0; background:var(--bg);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start;
      padding:24px 32px; gap:20px; transform:translateY(-8px); opacity:0; pointer-events:none;
      transition:opacity .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
    }
    .nav--open .nav__links{ opacity:1; transform:none; pointer-events:auto; }
    .nav__toggle{ display:block; }
    .hero{ padding:150px 0 70px; }
    .form-row{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .services__grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .why__grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .dash-card__stats{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .dmband__inner{ flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="nav" id="site-nav">
  <div class="wrap nav__inner">
    <a href="#top" class="nav__mark"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Brandify Business Solutions" class="nav__logo-icon">Brandify</a>
    <nav class="nav__links">
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#why">Why Us</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/brandify_biz_solutions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="nav__cta">DM us on Instagram</a>
    </nav>
    <button class="nav__toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu" aria-expanded="false">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

  <section class="hero" id="top">
    <div class="wrap hero__inner">
      <div>
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Brandify Business Solutions logo" class="hero__logo">
        <span class="eyebrow">Marketing &amp; Growth Studio · Navi Mumbai</span>
        <h1>We Brand. <span class="line-gold">We Grow.</span> We Deliver Results.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Empowering businesses with creative solutions and digital strategies that drive growth, visibility, and success.</p>
        <div class="hero__ctas">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/brandify_biz_solutions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary">DM us on Instagram</a>
          <a href="#services" class="btn btn--ghost">See our services</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dash-card">
        <div class="dash-card__head">
          <span>Leads Overview</span>
          <span class="dash-card__live"><span class="dot-pulse"></span>Live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card__stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__label">New Leads</span>
            <span class="stat__value">1,247</span>
            <span class="stat__delta">▲ 32.5%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__label">Appointments</span>
            <span class="stat__value">328</span>
            <span class="stat__delta">▲ 28.7%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__label">Revenue</span>
            <span class="stat__value">₹87,450</span>
            <span class="stat__delta">▲ 41.3%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card__chart">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 300 70" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <polyline points="0,55 40,50 80,52 120,35 160,40 200,20 240,26 300,8" fill="none" stroke="#D9A94E" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-card__foot">Daily leads. Real results. Growth of <strong>▲ 41.3%</strong> this quarter.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="problem" id="problem">
    <div class="wrap problem__inner">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Sound familiar?</span>
        <h2>No leads. Low sales. Wrong audience.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Low sales can slow your growth and limit your business potential. Still waiting for customers to come? That's not how business works today.</p>

        <div class="reasons">
          <div class="reason">
            <span class="reason__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="9" cy="8" r="3"/><path d="M3 20c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6s6 2.7 6 6"/><circle cx="17" cy="7" r="2.4"/><path d="M15.5 12.2c2.5.4 4.5 2.5 4.5 5.3"/></svg></span>
            <span class="reason__text">Targeting the Wrong Audience</span>
